snippet.title: Taphouse VR Teaser Trailer - BE THE BARTENDER!
snippet.description:
WISHLIST US NOW ON STEAM!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/591680/Taphouse_VR/

Welcome to the Taphouse October 17th 2017! Taphouse VR is a hilarious bartending simulator where you get to be a bartender for drunken dwarves. Mix recipe drinks and serve to survive!
